# CMD-Response

Chat-base `#CMD-Response` leverages the Gemini AI Model to generate textual responses from both image and text inputs.
This approach offers distinct advantages, such as providing command line responses for text and images without the need
to load complete DOM properties or rely on another web application.

# Start with Command

Clone
    
```
git clone https://github.com/kuldeep1A/CMD-Response.git
```

Credentials Key

```
echo [API_KEY] > credentials.ini
echo google_api_key="YOUR API KEY" >> credentials.ini
```

Start running `#CMD-Response`

```
cd CMD-Response\CMD-R-v
python start.py
```
